snippet.title: Wonderputt Trailer
snippet.description:
Wonderputt is the new online adventure golf game from dampgnat.com.  Free to play today at http://www.kongregate.com/games/dampgnat/wonderputt/?gamereferral=wonderputt

Voice over by Andrew Jacobs - Stilton Studios
Sound design by Dan Millidge - Redtone Media

View the development diary at http://www.dampgnat.com/wonderputtwip
